==To make a lemon battery you will need:== *A lemon *A penny *A nickel *Copper wire *An LED or calculator.
==Experiment:== *First, use some wire to cover a penny and other piece of wire on the nickel. *Insert the coins in the lemon and put the other sides of the wires in the sides of the LED. *Then you will see the electric power of the lemon flowing in the diode.
