==Introduction==

This is the branch of the [[A-level Chemistry]] book, designed to follow the [[w:Assessment and Qualifications Alliance|AQA]] specification. It is not endorsed by AQA. It will hopefully be useful as a revision guide, or for those seeking a basic grounding in the principles of the course.

