Recipe for MeenSuup:

1 meen, head and guts removed;
3 tomatoes, chopped;
2 limes;
1" piece ginger;
.5" piece galangal;
Water, sugar and salt to taste

Boil everything, then fling out the window. It probably wouldn't taste very good anyway.

(MeenSuup is actually a human being, not a food item. Don't be fooled by the name or the recipe!)

