I have created this book for the purpose of presenting detailed facts and information on the fictional universe of the ''Metal Gear'' series that would not usually be allowed on Wikipedia (such as writing detailed plot summary, fiction from an in-universe perspective, original research, etc.). The Wikipedia article [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metal_Gear_timeline Metal Gear timeline] which I wrote on 26th May 2006, and the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metal_Gear_timeline_compared_to_reality Metal Gear timeline compared to reality] article, were later deleted due to not meeting these guidelines, so I've added them to this book instead. This book is not intended to be a strategy guide, so please avoid adding such information. Feel free to contribute to this book or perhaps discuss any improvements this book may need. [[User:Jagged 85|Jagged 85]] 17:13, 10 November 2006 (UTC)

